*** Practicalli Study Group
   - Completed Visualising data science with Oz - A 7 video series that shows the use of Oz and Bulma CSS framework to create a dashboard of visualizations for the coronavirus in the UK.  Covering how to extract and transform data and how to deal with things when the data format changes.  Includes tips and examples to refactor a project as it grows.
   - Introduction to clojure.spec.alpha - start of a new video series cover how to use spec in the REPL and with Clojure projects
